Untar the package

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install


save the old files for their config data where ever you 
have put them in your directory tree and replace with 
these files if the version number has changed and edit 
them to add any needed configuration parameters that 
appear in the old files.

  examples/daemon.pl			labrea data collection
  Report/examples/page_report.plx	web data reports
  Get/examples/web_scan.pl		other sites
  examples/tell_me.pl			old rogue email notices
  DShield/examples/mail_dshield.pl	DShield reporting

check for a more recent version of:

	Report/examples/localTrojans.pl
	Get/examples/other_sites.txt

done!
